WITH RECURSIVE ranges (min_sum, max_sum, level) AS (

    VALUES (0, 100000, 1),     -- Начальное значение level = 1

    SELECT min_sum + 100000, max_sum + 100000, level + 1

    FROM ranges

WHERE max_sum < (SELECT max(total_amount) FROM bookings.bookings)
